{"tid":1157063,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"大陸食生蠔瀨嘢　薛家燕浴缸昏迷死過番生","createTime":"2019-05-16T04:16:38.000Z","updateTime":"2019-05-18T06:33:03.000Z","uid":141151,"like":592,"dislike":7,"uniUserReply":111,"replies":[{"pid":"f3a388d7d22767a50dfcfd3ef40ab4998b29bd76","tid":1157063,"uid":141151,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-16T04:16:38.000Z","msg":"大陸食生蠔瀨嘢 薛家燕浴缸昏迷死過番生<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/entertainment/20190516/bkn-20190516001709154-0516_00862_001.html?fbclid=IwAR1C0iVR5Wa8huI2BiXsDgP0pI9RM0dbrRN31QBzYVYv1l8GbZGglkJj0a8\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fentertainment%2F20190516%2Fbkn-20190516001709154-0516_00862_001.html%3Ffbclid%3DIwAR1C0iVR5Wa8huI2BiXsDgP0pI9RM0dbrRN31QBzYVYv1l8GbZGglkJj0a8&d=nKoZ4xrs0zkQ%2F022jTHdf8orGdVmFuHsJRpnpeioS7U%3D&h=e9037b22\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/entertainment/20190516/bkn-20190516001709154-0516_00862_001.html?fbclid=IwAR1C0iVR5Wa8huI2BiXsDgP0pI9RM0dbrRN31QBzYVYv1l8GbZGglkJj0a8</a><br />\n<br />\n藝人薛家燕在電視城錄影《流行經典50年》節目時透露，因食錯嘢搞到又屙又嘔：「母親節嗰日返咗大陸做商演，主辦單位請我食西餐，我就食咗啲生蠔，到第二日返嚟香港，個胃同個肚就好唔舒服，屙嘔咗好多次，<span style=\"color: red;\">有一次我忍唔住嘔咗落浴缸度，但醒嘅時候竟然發現自己塊面對住個浴缸底，手腳麻痹，隔籬就係啲嘔吐物，即係其實我係暈咗</span>，於是就慢慢爬番起身叫個女同工人，我諗都暈咗有分零兩分鐘，好彩個浴缸冇水，如果有水我就浸咗落去。」<br />\n<br />\n問之後可有入院檢查？她說：「冇呀！但有睇醫生。」樂觀的她笑言：「不過佢哋話我瘦咗好多，所以嚟緊六月尾嘅澳門演唱會，謝天華可以抱得起我啦！」<br />\n<br />\n另外，早前拍檔黎小田肺炎入院，她說：「佢出咗院，應該冇乜嘢，依家就休息緊，佢都話好掛住大家。（佢幾時復工？）未知。」"},{"pid":"080487b4193bb85dead71229c69d60535ee7ab00","tid":1157063,"uid":28765,"like":794,"dislike":4,"score":790,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-05-16T04:20:39.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://pic.pimg.tw/bustravelclub/113854934349.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fpic.pimg.tw%2Fbustravelclub%2F113854934349.jpg&h=b14bbfc6&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"847aa78045cccc6866732d4133985b5f3e851ba7","tid":1157063,"uid":186844,"like":279,"dislike":6,"score":273,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-0